# ============================================================================
# Deployment Exclusion Manifest
# ============================================================================
# Files and directories to EXCLUDE from ALL deployments (dev and prod)
# Format: One pattern per line (rsync --exclude format)
# Comments start with #
#
# This file is used by:
# - deploy.sh (package_release function)
# - export_public_package.sh (public release builds)
#
# Pattern examples:
#   __pycache__/     - Directory (trailing slash)
#   *.pyc            - All .pyc files
#   test_*.py        - Files matching pattern
#   logs             - Specific file or directory name
# ============================================================================

